  <brief_title>Can Valacyclovir Delay the Need for Initiation of Human Immunodeficiency Virus (HIV) Treatment in HIV-infected Individuals?</brief_title>
  <acronym>VALIDATE</acronym>
  <official_title>VALacyclovir In Delaying Antiretroviral Treatment Entry</official_title>
